        <item>
            <title>1.2.36</title>
            <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>https://getsetcraft.com/release-notes</sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 17:52:21 -0400</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.36</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.36</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changes

- Smoother navigation: the nav bar no longer flickers or shifts when you move between tabs.
- Your settings and one-time prompts now reliably persist between launches.
- Cleaner launch: the window opens dark instead of flashing white, and animated themes resolve in from the dark instead of showing the page first.
- Theme entrance animations now play once per launch instead of every dashboard visit.

Requires macOS 12 or later on Apple Silicon.
]]></description>
