            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## Changes

- New built-in Help Center: open it from the Help menu (Setcraft Help). It opens
  in its own window with a searchable set of offline guides, from getting started
  to troubleshooting.
- Fixed a case where adding an artist profile showed the upgrade prompt even when
  you had a paid seat free (the demo band was being counted against your limit).

